        <td>Split into per-tab provider classes</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>313 <code>: any</code> annotations</td>
        <td>Across all source files</td>
        <td>Medium</td>
        <td>Incremental typing with <code>strict: true</code> migration</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Test coverage ~4.6%</td>
        <td>3,807 test lines vs 82,013 source</td>
        <td>Large</td>
        <td>Establish 30% minimum. Prioritize services and planning.</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Hardcoded ID patterns (ARMOIN-XXX)</td>
        <td>entities/*.ts, validators</td>
        <td>Small</td>
        <td>Make configurable per workspace</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>

