      <div class="card" style="border-left:3px solid var(--accent-teal);">
        <h4>🔄 Live Collaboration Mode</h4>
        <p>Extend RealTimeUpdateSystem with CRDT-based conflict resolution for multi-user simultaneous planning. Real-time cursors and presence indicators.</p>
        <span class="badge badge-teal">High Value</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="border-left:3px solid var(--accent-blue);">
        <h4>📊 Predictive Analytics Dashboard</h4>
        <p>Use TelemetryCollector data to build ML-powered burndown predictions, bottleneck detection, and team performance insights.</p>
        <span class="badge badge-blue">High Value</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="border-left:3px solid var(--accent-green);">
        <h4>🎯 Natural Language Planning</h4>
        <p>Expand NLPlanningParser to support full natural language project creation: "Create a login system with OAuth, 2FA, and SSO" → auto-generates Epic/Story/Task tree.</p>
        <span class="badge badge-green">Medium Value</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="border-left:3px solid var(--accent-yellow);">
        <h4>🔌 Plugin Marketplace</h4>
        <p>Build on AIKitManager to create a searchable marketplace for AI kits, skills, personas, and instruction sets. Community contributions with ratings.</p>
        <span class="badge badge-yellow">High Value</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="border-left:3px solid var(--accent-peach);">
        <h4>📱 Mobile Companion App</h4>
        <p>Progressive Web App using MCP HTTP transport for mobile planning review, approval workflows, and notifications on the go.</p>
        <span class="badge badge-peach">Medium Value</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="border-left:3px solid var(--accent-red);">
        <h4>🔐 SOC 2 Compliance Mode</h4>
