        <span class="badge badge-red">Enterprise</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="border-left:3px solid var(--accent-mauve);">
        <h4>🌐 Multi-Repo Orchestration</h4>
        <p>Extend Leader Election to coordinate planning across multiple repositories. Shared epics spanning codebases.</p>
        <span class="badge badge-mauve">Medium Value</span>
